  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Fountain of Youth was hidden away. Nonetheless, it is fated that a Usurper will slay the Ageless and unearth it once more.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FOUNTAINS is an action-RPG about fighting your way through a maze-like interconnected world. You'll take the role of a hooded stranger, recently imprisoned by a tyrannical regime. Will you escape and uncover the mysteries of this war-torn empire? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras/d04dd3750a71c39a201698b49ec6e66d.poster.avif?t=1769777114\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras/d04dd3750a71c39a201698b49ec6e66d.webm?t=1769777114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras/d04dd3750a71c39a201698b49ec6e66d.mp4?t=1769777114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world of FOUNTAINS is designed as one giant dungeon. It is a tightly packed labyrinth which twists and loops back on itself. You'll constantly find new items, powers and upgrades to unlock new parts of the world.  <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras/ba5cf89787cef3e26b8974f4418c7f52.avif?t=1769777114\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras_big/ba5cf89787cef3e26b8974f4418c7f52.avif?t=1769777114 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FOUNTAINS also features an online message system. Leave hints throughout the world to help out your fellow players, or trick them into doing something foolish!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras/9bd09329c7f3309be795658dfefd0ebf.avif?t=1769777114\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras_big/9bd09329c7f3309be795658dfefd0ebf.avif?t=1769777114 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master tight, high-skilled combat and defeat punishing bosses against all odds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find new abilities and tools to help you to defend yourself and to traverse the world </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Meet many strange characters, both hostile and friendly </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Secrets are everywhere, so always keep an eye out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Fountain of Youth was hidden away. Nonetheless, it is fated that a Usurper will slay the Ageless and unearth it once more.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FOUNTAINS is an action-RPG about fighting your way through a maze-like interconnected world. You'll take the role of a hooded stranger, recently imprisoned by a tyrannical regime. Will you escape and uncover the mysteries of this war-torn empire? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras/d04dd3750a71c39a201698b49ec6e66d.poster.avif?t=1769777114\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras/d04dd3750a71c39a201698b49ec6e66d.webm?t=1769777114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras/d04dd3750a71c39a201698b49ec6e66d.mp4?t=1769777114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world of FOUNTAINS is designed as one giant dungeon. It is a tightly packed labyrinth which twists and loops back on itself. You'll constantly find new items, powers and upgrades to unlock new parts of the world.  <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras/ba5cf89787cef3e26b8974f4418c7f52.avif?t=1769777114\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras_big/ba5cf89787cef3e26b8974f4418c7f52.avif?t=1769777114 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FOUNTAINS also features an online message system. Leave hints throughout the world to help out your fellow players, or trick them into doing something foolish!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras/9bd09329c7f3309be795658dfefd0ebf.avif?t=1769777114\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841240/extras_big/9bd09329c7f3309be795658dfefd0ebf.avif?t=1769777114 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master tight, high-skilled combat and defeat punishing bosses against all odds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find new abilities and tools to help you to defend yourself and to traverse the world </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Meet many strange characters, both hostile and friendly </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Secrets are everywhere, so always keep an eye out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
